      <title>法官支持迪士尼拒绝基金对代理文件的要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/judge-sides-with-disney-in-refusing-fund-demand-for-proxy-files</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特拉华州一名法官得出结论，华特迪士尼公司无需交出有关其与 ValueAct 资本管理公司的关系以及这位激进投资者在该娱乐巨头董事会激烈的代理权争夺战中所扮演的角色的记录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/judge-sides-with-disney-in-refusing-fund-demand-for-proxy-files</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:58:12 GMT</pubDate>
