      <title>淡水河谷任命矿业资深人士乌斯马尔领导基本金属业务转型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/vale-picks-mining-veteran-usmar-to-lead-base-metals-turnaround</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，巴西金属生产商淡水河谷 (Vale SA) 已选定资深矿业高管肖恩·乌斯马尔 (Shaun Usmar) 执掌其基本金属部门，以期提高铜和镍的产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/vale-picks-mining-veteran-usmar-to-lead-base-metals-turnaround</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:36:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
